text: Sripal Singh Yadav is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Lok Sabha, the lower house of the Parliament of India as a member of the Janata Dal. ==References== ==External links== *Official biographical sketch in Parliament of India website Category:1942 births Category:Lok Sabha members from Uttar Pradesh Category:9th Lok Sabha members Category:10th Lok Sabha members Category:Janata Dal politicians Category:Living people
